description: When the Russian mafia meets the Var underworld! Leo is surrounded: Marlene wants a baby. As for Tonton, he's waiting on his boat for Marlene's fit to be over...So, when a Russian heavy hitter is looking for a middleman for a meeting between him and the bosses of the Var underworld, Leo considers it to be a real vacation in the sun of Toulon, maybe not...
name: Tropézienne dum dum

description:
The explosive meeting between crime fiction and fantasy !

A plane crash. Hundreds of deaths.

All the instruments on board allegedly stopped functioning without any reason.

An accident? Or the work of a more inhuman, more omnipotent and more complex mind?

For FBI agents Fischer and Fallow, some files are never closed...
name: No Such Agency

description:
Some cases are never closed! A breathtaking conclusion!

After spending years fighting against extraterrestrial entities, our heroes have to face a conspiracy that has freed another sort of entity: an Artificial Intelligence. Fischer, whose brain has been corrupted, is the ideal link between the two worlds. Will the friendship of our heroes survive this new trial? And will the world survive, too?
name: Mirrors glass

description:
Nils is a sparkling ecological saga halfway between the Norse legends and Miyazaki’s works.

According to old legends, a world beyond matter exists, peopled by luminous beings without whom this matter would remain inert. So when the Northern Territories, formerly flourishing, change into arid lands, the legends come back… With his father, young Nils tries to solve the mystery and goes searching for the luminous beings who guide him towards a neighbouring kingdom with advanced technology…
name: Les Élémentaires
Mon frère c'est pas un cadeau !!!
